unplug the battery from the wall and the battery pack
plug the battery into the amplifier (battery is the bottom box, amplifier is the top box) 
one chamber has no battery, connect the amplifier directly to the plug
connect the head box into the amplifier using the rubbon until the ears/tabs come out
turn amplifier and the head box on, lights will turn green
make sure windows is running
turn on monitor and press eye icon (on the computer outside of the chamber)
c hange the monitor in the chamber to DVI to show subject their signal
Turn off the light in the chamber 
close the door

To launch the program:
On the computer outside of the chamber start rec ording by pressing the green play button 
On the stimulus generating computer, select run on matlab
start recording signals
save the erp file using the subject number 
